> On Jun 5, 2018, at 11:59 AM, Samsiddhi Bhattacharjee <sb1 at nibmg.ac.in> wrote:
> 
> I was thinking to have an onAttach  mentioning the issue and directing the user to use the devel version to get around the issue...is that possible?
